Description: # kewpie
        KEyWord PIckEr with tf-idf
        
        Work in Progress.
        
        ## Installation
        ```bash
        pip install kewpie
        ```
        
        ## Basic Usage
        ```py
        from kewpie import KwPicker
        
        docs = [
            "I am a cat.",
            "I am a dog."
        ]
        
        picker = KwPicker.build(docs, savedir='/dir/to/save/model/')
        
        sentence = "I am a cat."
        span, keyword = picker.get_keywords(sentence)
        
        print(keyword)  # -> 'cat'
        ```
        
